          "x": 234,
          "y": 1008
        },
        {
          "angle": 0,
          "height": 152,
          "symHeight": 19.8955223880597,
          "symWidth": 15.80746268656716,
          "text": "THE  HIDDEN  SECT  IS GREAT !  THE  SECT  OF THE  HIDDEN  WORLD ! IT'S  MUCH  BETTER THAN  SOME  RANDOM SECT  NAME !",
